71 /*========== Extern Function Implementations ================================*/
72 extern void DIAG_Sbc(
73  DIAG_ID_e diagId,
74  DIAG_EVENT_e event,
75  const DIAG_DATABASE_SHIM_s *const kpkDiagShim,
76  uint32_t data) {
77  FAS_ASSERT(diagId < DIAG_ID_MAX);
78  FAS_ASSERT((event == DIAG_EVENT_OK) || (event == DIAG_EVENT_NOT_OK) || (event == DIAG_EVENT_RESET));
79  FAS_ASSERT(kpkDiagShim != NULL_PTR);
80 
81  if (diagId == DIAG_ID_SBC_FIN_STATE) {
82  if (event == DIAG_EVENT_RESET) {
83  kpkDiagShim->pTableError->mcuSbcFinError = false;
84  }
85  if (event == DIAG_EVENT_NOT_OK) {
86  kpkDiagShim->pTableError->mcuSbcFinError = true;
87  }
88  } else if (diagId == DIAG_ID_SBC_RSTB_STATE) {
89  if (event == DIAG_EVENT_RESET) {
90  kpkDiagShim->pTableError->mcuSbcRstbError = false;
91  }
92  if (event == DIAG_EVENT_NOT_OK) {
93  kpkDiagShim->pTableError->mcuSbcRstbError = true;
94  }
95  }
96 }
